      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000757",
          "label": "Side linings installed on both side cowls",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "6. Installation of front side garnishes on both sides",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000757",
          "label": "Installation of front side garnishes on both sides",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "7. Center lower cover mounting",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000780",
          "label": "Center lower cover mounting",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "8. Driver Lower Cover Installation",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000771",
          "label": "Driver Lower Cover Installation",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "9. Equalizer Installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "703_3.0_jpn_11035965_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Attach the adjusting nut (B) to the equalizer (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "10. Parking brake adjustment",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000684",
          "label": "Parking brake adjustment",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "11. Equalizer cover installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "703_3.0_jpn_11035966_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Install the equalizer cover (A). Restore the carpet in the center of the floor."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Parking brake cable B installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "703_3.0_jpn_11035967_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Install the parking brake cable B to the backing plate (A). Attach the cable clip (D) to the cable insertion slot (C) on the back side of the backing plate. Connect parking brake cable B to the parking brake lever on the brake shoe. Install the brake shoes.",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000697",
          "label": "Install the brake shoes.",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Do not forcibly twist or strongly bend the parking brake cable. A deformed or damaged cable may cause malfunction or cut damage."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "Align the protrusion (E) on the parking brake cable holder with the groove (F) on the backing plate insert."
        },
        {
          "text": "Align the protrusion (E) on the parking brake cable holder with the groove (F) on the backing plate insert."
        },
        {
          "text": "Push the cable holder until the groove (G) in the cable holder fits into the groove (H) in the cable insertion slot."
        },
        {
          "text": "Push the cable holder until the groove (G) in the cable holder fits into the groove (H) in the cable insertion slot."
        },
        {
          "text": "To install the cable clip, insert the straight part of the clip (I) into the cutout in the cable insertion area and securely fasten the parking brake cable holder."
        },
        {
          "text": "To install the cable clip, insert the straight part of the clip (I) into the cutout in the cable insertion area and securely fasten the parking brake cable holder."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "703_3.0_jpn_11035968_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "703_3.0_jpn_11035969_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "5",
      "text": "Install parking brake cable B. For 4WD vehicles, tighten together with No.2 propeller shaft protector mounting nut (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "703_3.0_jpn_11035970_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "6",
      "text": "Pull the parking brake cable B into the interior. Install the grommet (A). When installing grommets, make sure that they do not float or come off."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Wire Guide Base Mounting"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "703_3.0_jpn_11035971_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Install parking brake cable B to the equalizer (A). Install the wire guide base (C)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Brake drum installation",
      "refs": [
